data.description: Explore this PRE-INSPECTED,  2-story home in the golf course community of Eagle Hills and just 200 feet from a pet-friendly walking trail system. Inside, you'll find a grand 2-story entry, spacious living room with a bay window, and a cozy gas fireplace. A versatile den with French doors is perfect for a home office or library. The adjacent dining room and kitchen feature stainless steel appliances, a large island, maple cabinets, and hardwood floors. Pella designer windows, an extra deep 3-bay garage wired for EV, and a generous corner lot on a quiet cul-de-sac add to the appeal. Every bedroom includes walk-in closets! The finished basement offers a built-in bar, living area with gas fireplace, flex room, and a 3/4 bath. Brand new interior paint adds a modern touch! Outside you’ll find a beautiful composite deck added in 2022, and a raised garden bed. Updates include exterior paint (‘18), water softener (‘17), refrigerator (‘16), gas range (‘18), HVAC ('18).
